      "content": "okay i hear you, but i already have some extra strength ibuprofen in my cabinet and i really dont want to bother my doctor for just a headache. it's not that bad, just a dull ache. isn't a little bit of ibuprofen fine as long as i don't take too much? i just need something to help me get through the afternoon.",
